content.detailedDescription:
Im going to try and condense this as much as i can and i apologize if its too long.  a friend and me set off last saturday evening to camp and squirrel hunt sunday morning.  the location is the mark twain national forest between bellview and bixby off highway 32.  we arrived after dark around 9 in my explorer  and quickly had a fire going. we had planned sleeping in front bucket seats as we had many times before. at about 10:30 i jumped on roof of explorer and he on the hood as we had an open area to starwatch. my friend had placed his gun with its site against car between passenger door and front right quarter panel.  it would have to be lifted back to pick it up.  he showed me where he had left the the gun and said it was loaded.  i want to add that the entire time we are out there, we were never out of each others sight at all. his dog, a beagle/husky mix wandered the perimeter a few times but mainly slept quietly in middle seat of car on passenger side.  all doors to the car were opened except for the two passenger side doors.  the only thing in back of car was my friends wal-mart bag with some clothes and his medicine.  back lid as open. we were at least 6 miles into the woods off the highway. literally no houses for miles. so,as we are chatting at around midnight, i see a dark object out of the corner of my eye to my right, followed by 2-3 loud thumps. i immediately felt something was thrown at us.  nothing could have fallen from tree above us because it was opened of any trees. we both heard it to our right. again, we knew something out of ordinary had happened so i asked my friend if he had his still by him.  he reached for it and it was not there. as we get down off car we see the gun is 2-3 feet away from car with the handle broken off. it was flat where we were, with a small pitch to the front right ofcar.  the gun had fallen opposite the pitch. as strange as this was, the gun was laying about a foot and half towards rear of car. again opposite of pitch or slant of hill.  we have spent many nights camping and hunting. many together, with family even alone. whatever landed was not a branch or tree. after the thumps there was silence. we looked all over, nothing. we became debunkers and were still going to stay. we dropped his gun around 10 times before the handle would break off.  and my friend was forcing it to the ground. as we looked for what could have landed and made the thumps and could not explain it, we thought it would be better to just leave the situation alone and head home. so we did just that. so we threw what few things we had into the car and i got in and started it. my friend went to the back of the car to check his bag and a bottle of medicine had been opened and was laying upside down in the bag with only 4 pills under it. he believes 8-12 were missing. he had taken his night meds earlier and i was  there near him. went through car thoroughly and everything we had taken to the woods and nothing turned up. so we leave.  as we leave through forest i notice on my left the glare of my headlights in the forest. at one point ??I noticed what appeared be a bluish white light through the forest moving at our speed then falling back then speeding up to our speed. about 3 times i  saw it and it was gone. i continued to watch for it and making sure it wasn’t the glare of my lights that i saw.
that’s about it. wev been trying to replay and debunk things ever since.  we don’t drink and consider ourselves pretty experienced in the woods.
content.summary: Dark object loud thud landing, things out of place and retangle lights observed.

content.detailedDescription: The two videos that i have submitted freak me out especially when i put them in slow motion. those were taken on sept 16, 2015. there were other nights as well that i was out taking pictures and taking videos. when i reviewed some of my other videos, i kept hitting the start and stop button. every time i hit the stop button i would take a screen shot from my phone to see the detail. some of my other videos i've been having trouble downloading them from my phone. i must say that i am totally freaked out. different times i have been almost hysterical when i think about it. the one video of the red lights flashing throughout the video are kinda creepy. when put in slow motion, the very beginning looks like a giant eye blinking. there are clicking sounds, other sounds like squeaking doors and other sounds. i hardly know what to think. i have always believed since childhood. i've had many sightings throughout my 53 years of life. but just recently after seeing the two videos that i have submitted and not remember taking them, makes me even more of a believer. i'm extremely nervous and feel like i can't hardly deal with any of it anymore.
content.summary: I noticed a light like a star but it also had red and blue blinking lights. i told my friend and husband to come look.

content.detailedDescription: As i was at the back of our house, i heard a humming noise. i was four at the time. as i turned around, there was a very large ship hovering next to a tree and a door opened. the craft is of a very dark color bearing strange patterns that didn't seem to be writing but construction patterns. as the door opened, an entity came out and stood on it as a robotic arm picked me up. this entity was dressed with a shiny black cloth and had what i believe to be a mask that made it look like it had a beak. after that i remember sort of waking up in a table and something being put in my back. they told me it was a star and being a kid thats what i believed. i remember seeing smaller beings walking by but my vision was blurred. i remember waking up in a grass field about 200 meters from where i was and the grass had been pushed down like a crop circle type. i ran home and explained my parents what had happened. the neighbors at the time saw the craft and reported the house shaking as it went by and the lights flickering. the same happened at my house. we were poor and didn't have a camera so no photos were taken. i am now a sargent in the army with aviation background. if more information is needed please contact me asap.
content.summary: When i was four playing outside saw entity in craft and after abduction woke up far away. many witnesses

content.detailedDescription: I was laying with my head on the back garden path facing to the left of my house when i saw to my right a wingless rusty red cigar shape.It had 5 circular windows and it was moving very slowly and silently from my right to my left in around ten minutes before it dissapeared behind my neighbours house i wasnt allowed to walk off around the streets at the time.The port holes were opaque black with a bit of movement inside couldnt see in them they were too far away to distinguish what was inside but definately movement i was aged between 5 and 7 years old at the time and so made mental notes as to what i was seeing because id never seen something like that before and somehow knew even at that age it would be important to remember what it looked like.. it happened between 1983-1985 sorry i cant be anymore exact
content.summary: Rusty red cigar shaped 5 windows drifting at very low speed from my right to left

content.detailedDescription: This is video i filmed on my phone camera and the quality is poor but it still gives a fairly accurate depiction of what i saw this past thursday evening of september 10 at approximately 845 pm. this is video filmed over the atlantic ocean in cape hatteras north carolina on a night with very gusty winds.  these lights in the video were many miles out over the sea, miles high in the sky.  my brother and i were sitting on the deck of our cottage when we noticed these bright lights appearing miles out at sea up in the sky in perfect alignment but the distance between them was a larger difference than it appears on the video, so if these were drones they would have to be quite large.  it was very windy and it made the camera footage shake alot.  these were not planes, helicopters, stars, flares or chinese lanterns.   i have concluded that this must be either a type of military practice maneuvering (drones) or in fact a ufo.    many more appeared over the next 20 minutes in various formations appearing, disappearing, and reappearing.  my niece and nephew also filmed them on there ipads and i ll post that below also. it was alot of fun to watch.  they had an orange orb like appearance and at any time there could be 5 showing at one time.
content.summary: Ufo sighting over cape hatteras north carolina on september 10 2015

content.detailedDescription:
I have been observing multiple ufos in the sky for over a year in the beeville area. i do not know what these objects are. tonight i was able to get good digital photos of one of these objects and also had several eye wittnesses with me that saw the objects in the sky. i am in my front yard when i am observing these objects. i look for them most every night. a licensed pilot/aircraft mechanic who is a personal friend of mine here,  has also seen these objects and could not identify what they were.

i first noticed the objects because of their sequential flashing red/blue-green/white lights. i am a usaf/texas air national guard aircraft technician and am very familiar with aircraft. what i am seeing are not aircraft nor satellites in orbit. i do no know what they are. 

i first saw the object i observed/monitored tonight above my neighbor's treetop at approximately 265 degrees west  hovering. it then descended moved doward to aproximately 280 degrees northwest, hovered at the lower altitube fore approximately 10 minutes, then moved away in the same direction slowly until it went out of sight.

the photos we have indicate a disc-shaped saucer type craft with domes on top and bottom. you can clearly see the saucer shaped craft when you zoom in on the photos along with the light (s)at mid upper section. i would liketo share these photos with mufon in private for now. 

i would like to get a telephone call from mufon so i could describe in more detail what i and others are seeing/have seen. i think it would be worthwhile and beneficial for mufon to observe these ufos for themselves and photograph them. 

as for my feeling about what i am seeing, i am curious as to what they are.
i am a married, stable professional/technical male person and i have civilian/military aviation backgrounds. i have had an interest aeronautical sciences and space travel since i was a child. i cannot identify these objects i am seeing. i'm not afraid of them and believe they are exactly what i call them - unidentified flying objects.
content.summary: Multiple ufos sighted - all look the same

content.summary: Clear skies; shadow displayed on ground running along side road. no object in sky

content.detailedDescription:
At about 8:15 p.M., i was in my back yard stooped down with a flashlight looking for my boat trailer's model information. i suddenly heard a very loud helicopter approaching from the southeast. i looked up to see if i could spot it, but wasn't able to see it due to the tree cover in my back yard. 

because it sounded so low and loud, i was curious to see what was going on. to get a better view, i quickly walked approximately 50 feet to my driveway for an unobstructed view of the sky. as i got to the driveway, i saw a helicopter flying quite low and fast emerge overhead.

as i watched the helicopter fly rapidly toward the north-northwest, i noticed a bright light flying ahead of the helicopter in the same direction and at a similar altitude. the helicopter appeared to be flying at the same speed as the object.

what immediately struck me as odd is that the object was silent and there were no flashing aviation lights. by contrast, the helicopter's aviation lights were easily visible throughout the event.

both the object and helicopter continued flying north-northwest. after about 20 seconds, the object was obscured by the tree line in the distance. a few seconds later, the helicopter was also obscured.
content.summary: Observed loud, extremely low-flying helicopter following an unidentified object (light) that made no sound and had no flashing aviation lights.

content.detailedDescription: It was around 11:30 pm est when i was looking out of my bedroom window. i noticed the object because it was stationary, fairly bright, and had pulsating lights. at first, i thought it was a helicopter or plane, but the night was completely still. there would have been sound if it had been one of them. it hovered over or around another house for about 15-30 seconds, and then it began to fly in my general direction. it flew horizontal to me and away past my field of vision. i was shocked to see the object, and it left me concerned afterwards.
content.summary: Rectangular object with lights hovered over building and then flew away.

content.detailedDescription: On friday, september 18th, my mother and i were driving from new jersey to maryland. it was early morning (somewhere between 8a-9a) and i was driving, my mother was in the passenger seat. we were on i95 when i looked up at a large grouping of clouds passing overhead.  the clouds themselves weren't unusual but an object within the clouds caught my eye. it was a perfect white triangle, completely solid, and i thought it was strange because the clouds it was surrounded by were thin and wispy (i could see the blue sky thru the clouds). i pointed it out to my mother and she thought it was odd as well. we continued to watch the object. the clouds eventually rolled away and all that was left was blue sky and the white triangle. my mother and i continued to watch the triangle as it hovered over the highway. after a few minutes it began changing shape. it was no longer triangle shaped. the wings seemed to spread apart and the object had a longer, cylindrical shape. the shape continued to change like a transformer trying to figure out where all its pieces belong. my mother attempted to take pictures of the object but had a hard time capturing it. the photos that she did take look a white streak in the sky.  after 20-30 minutes the object disappeared.  later (maybe 10 minutes), a large helicopter flew overhead, coming from the direction where the object had been. we did not see it again.
content.summary: White triangle shape over highway. changed shape then disappeared

content.detailedDescription: My wife and i were coming home from a store when i noticed a weird yellowish light above a field near home it looked like a small ball of fire like seeing fire in a glass ball it was defending slowly on a slight angle i thought it would land but then leveled off and continued west i guess about 20or30feet off the ground moved across the field when it neared the other side of the field it began to rise and continued west i tried to get a video on wife's cell but either i could not get the lens trained on the object or it wasn't putting off enough light for the camera to pick up then we lost sight of it so we turned around and tried to find it again but the trees in our area grow close to the roads and make long range sight problematic at best after making several turns we did spot it again for a few seconds then we lost it behind more trees.After when we got home i did check video but all i had was a recording that didn't show what we saw and me sounding very excited. after getting home my wife said she thought she saw an arm extended from the main ball with small red lights along it. this i didn't notice but in trying to get the cell phone out and start recording i would not doubt i may have missed something.  this was very exciting for both of us as well as very strange.
content.summary: Wife and i driving home i notice small fireball slowly dec end then level then rise and move west

content.detailedDescription: Tonight while driving back to my girlfriends house i noticed a strange red/orange ball in the sky near lake mohawk in sparta new jersey.It was clear tonight, 63 degrees f and had my sun roof fully open around 7:55 pm.I pulled over to stop my car off route 181,its was hovering in pulsating, and jerky motions, no blue or green lights like a small plane will have , floating, bouncing like i guess. i started filming with my smart android phone in between watching through my sun roof trying my best to hold the cell phone steady it was very interesting that although it appeared red-orange to me the video on my cell looks mostly white with occasional red -orange. although fussy it was not a plane, helicopter, or blimp, this was very unusual for sure.Eventually i noticed it fairly quickly rose to a great height in a waver uneven climb, so it was then too small to see anymore. i thought it was neat as i haven't seen anything like this since a sighting 25 or so years ago.I felt privileged to capture video and observe this object, excitedly called my girlfriend to tell her, she liked the video even though it barley captured what i saw with my eyes.
content.summary: Observed red orange ball in sky stopped my car watched and filmed on my smart phone video

content.detailedDescription:
I'm a high school yearbook photographer. i was photographing a girl's varsity soccer game at saddle brook nj high school. during down time i was looking up at the sky and noticed a contrail of a jet, but couldn't see the jet itself. i zoomed out with my 300mm lens to take a pic of the jet. it was flying at a very high altitude. i put the camera in manual focus mode. this is something you have to do when photographing high flying objects. i took a couple pictures. i zoomed in on my nikon d7100 lcd display to look at the jet when i noticed there was something in front of it. (the jet was flying in a westerly direction) i took some more photos trying to get the object in frame. i could not see it with my eye. i needed the 300mm lens trying to see it. i took several pics. i looked at the display on my nikon, zooming in to try to determine what the object was. i was baffled. i pointed my camera skyward and could not find the object again. it was gone.

at home i looked at the silhouette of the jet. i noticed it had squared wings. i looked at some stock u2 photos. it looks like a u2.

i have 10 pics of the jet and the object. i will attach some highly zoomed in photos for you.

i've been a sports photographer for 8 years. i am very camera savy, i know my cameras.

whatever this is, it baffles me.

i was sitting by myself, behind the goal during the game. the field runs east/west so i had to sit at the western edge to have the sun at my back for the photos. i don't know if anyone else saw it, it was very high and impossible to see with the unaided eye.

i was freaked out when i saw what i had captured on my camera.
content.summary: While photographing a high flying jet i noticed something else in the photograph.

content.altitude: Over 500 Feet (under cloudcover), Over 500 Feet (no cloudcover)
content.detailedDescription: A friend and i observe an object for the past 10 months. we first noticed it by chance, talking and looking at the stars. it is in the same place, it has changed shape at times. once going from a ball shape to having a spike shape bottom and then changing back. it does move and it has vanished before. we see it at about f8:30pm to about 3am. it does not scare us, but it has made my heart race a couple of times. we have noticed that it has appeared to flash colors and another object flashed back one night. this only occurred once but the other object also appeared to be on a straight line. hard to explain, but clearly not a plane, helicopter, or star. it has skipped a few nights and approximate a month and a half, but other than that - every night!
content.summary: We observe this almost every night for the past 10 months!

content.detailedDescription:
Out on my deck letting dogs out
that it was the only thing in the sky!
a planet
it was at first stationary then went to the left slowly then straight away from me and very fast came right back to where if first was above me as high as planes would pass over...It was windy out no sound. i wasnt scared because i thought it might be a personal drone then i thought that drone can cause a plane accident .. it hovered for a while i felt like it noticed me then went over to i-24 and came back to the same position the very quickly shot off back to i-24 until i could not see it.. bright red and blue lights pulsing..
it lasted for around 20 minutes.. 
as days go by it bothers me to think it was maybe a ufo i don't think personal drones can go that high.  i've posted things on my fb and on the city's facebook asking people to let me know if it was a drone

content.detailedDescription:
I live in glendale ca. my husband and i were celebrating our anniversary outside on our deck overlooking downtown los angeles. at 7:40pm i spotted what i thought was a meteor and shouted for my husband to grab the kids before it "flamed out". as soon as my husband saw it we both noticed the meteor was getting very big and started to panic a little about how large the impact would be as it approached downtown. 

at the same time we're spotting the object our neighbors who were having a labor day party with about 12-15 people (also with the same view of downtown)spotted the object as well and started taking pictures. right away the object began moving like a hummingbird and everyone instantly knew this was no meteor. after hovering in a stationary position for a few seconds, a second and identical light appeared right next to it giving everyone watching a huge shock! we all watched predicting the two lights would merge, but they didn't. the second light disappeared and the first light descended below our view. we of course went to social media right away and sure enough there were tons of people who were posting videos to youtube and tweeting about the incident.

it was an amazing and beautiful display. we feel lucky to have witnessed it.  

**important to note**
the youtube video attached below is not mine. its a compilation of a few i found. i unfortunately was too stunned in the moment to grab a phone #fail
content.summary: Labor day weekend. two ufo's over south los angeles. witnessed by many

content.detailedDescription: I was in my backyard using a believed contact method projecting tones into the airwaves. i looked over at the west mountain and there was a very bright flashing circle of light which was changing from red to white to blue. at first i thought it was another plane but as i kept watching it i was seeing it descend low to the ground then it moved right out of my view due to the housing complexes around then it came back and hovered for approx. 15 minutes which is when it descended again until i couldn't see it since my fence was in my way. i shined a red laser into the vicinity (carefully checking for any aircrafts beforehand of course) that is when it came back up but it was staying the exact same color of red just 500x brighter. it had stayed this color for about a full minute before it burnt out and when it came back to view it was flashing the lights again. the last thing i had seen was it dip back down out of view. possibly landed? kept my sights in that direction for the next hour.. never noticed it leave.
content.summary: Flashing different colors on the west mountain  when i shined my red laser in the vicinity it went out then came back same color of red then went back to multiple colors

content.detailedDescription:
My wife was giving our daughter and grandchildren a ride home. (7:35 pm, sept. 22. 2015) as they drove out of the driveway i looked to the north and directly up the river canyon, at an unknown distance (i would guess 15-20 miles at approx. 15 degrees above horizon) i observed two very bright white lights blinking back and forth, then they stopped and a light at the same level 5 degrees or so to the left blinked on and off for 4-5 seconds then went out, back to the right side (same angle and elevation)of the first two for a similar display.  then back the middle two... this went on for 3-5 minutes. there were four very distinct light sources, all apparently at the same elevation and distance from me. there was no apparent change in position during this time. they were considerable brighter than nav lights, and resembled landing lights aimed directly in my direction.(i am a licensed pilot). after they disappeared i noticed a commercial airliner traverse the area-- it was considerably dimmer, blinking, and at approximately 30 degrees of elevation from my vantage point. unfortunately i could not call anyone, nor take pictures of the lights as my family was in transit home. i hope i am not the only witness, but i'm the only witness i know of at this time.

the lights were spaced kind of like this in the night sky:

                     *            * *             *
this was basically true north of my location. i really enjoyed the sighting and told my wife about it when she returned.....
content.summary: Four lights took turns turning on and off in the northern sky from my home.  two in the middle and one left by two fingers and on on the right side by the same distance.  lights took turns on and off for 3-5 seconds

content.detailedDescription:
1. i was driving to look at a possible property to rent on back roads out of town with a friend. we had just finished a conversation about a possible ufo my friend had seen a few years back in indiana.

2. as we were talking we were periodically glancing up at the sky and it appeared right in view out of the windshield. i thought it was a falling star so it caught our attention.

3. it looked very similar to falling stars i have seen in the past.

4. it seemed to just appear and fall downward quickly at a slight angle. it had no tail and was a bright green.

5. it seemed very coincidental due to the conversation we were having at the time. the conversation we were having had us looking up at the stars for fun.

6. the object seemed to just appear, fall and then vanished instantly. it did not trail off or fade at all. it was as bright at its first appearance as it was before it disappeared.
content.summary: It looked similar to a falling star with no tail but a bright green orb

content.detailedDescription: At approximately 2130 hours, sunday night, september 20. 2015 i observed an object in the sky that was not moving at all.  it appeared very far in the distant sky and had a blue glow color.  i went inside and got my camera, and began to take pictures, having to zoom in to get the pictures.  as i began to take pictures it began to move across the sky.  i heard no noise, or saw no trail.  it was a mostly a cloud-less night, and i saw other stars in the sky, and this was definitely different than a star as it appeared blue rather than white like a star.  my family and i watched it for about 15 minutes, and then i went inside to put the pictures on my computer.  a few minutes later i went back outside, and the object was directly over-head our house, high in the sky.  it then move to the north-west sky, and disappeared.  i couldn't locate it again.  i was able to get some still pictures and a video.
content.summary: Blue glowing objects
